sive feature is now depreciated and you are encouraged to move things over to the newer and easier to use mobile features. For now the Responsive feature is still there and unchanged. But it won&#8217;t be developed further.</p>\n<h2>Changes</h2>\n<div class="shortcode-unorderedlist arrow">\n<ul>\n<li>[new] Option to disable dynamic mode on mobile devices</li>\n<li>[new] Added &#8216;Desktop&#8217; option to Mobile adverts</li>\n<li>[new] Optionally let advertisers use the Mobile adverts option</li>\n<li>[new] Basic sortable columns for most dashboard tables</li>\n<li>[fix] Region selection not working for advertisers</li>\n<li>[change] Responsive feature is now deprecated</li>\n<li>[i18n] Updated translation files</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2>Golfing in the mountains</h2>\n<p>In the Philippines, that&#8217;s possible. In Puerto Galera there is a 9 hole golf course. The other day I went there for the view&#8230; It&#8217;s about 800m above sea-level. The view down to Puerto Galera and White Beach is awesome!</p>\n<p><a href="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/puerto-galera-800m-up.jpg" rel="lightbox-1"><img src="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/puerto-galera-800m-up-1024x768.jpg" alt="puerto-galera-800m-up" width="1024" height="768" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-9058" srcset="https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/puerto-galera-800m-up-300x225.jpg 300w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/puerto-galera-800m-up-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://ajdg.solutions/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/puerto-galera-800m-up.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:48:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:3:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"dat